<plot>An illegitimate Australian Chinese girl returns to her extended family in Singapore after her mother's death, to claim the inheritance that is rightly her's. However, she witnesses the murder of her grandmother whom she hates, and she gets into an accident herself and loses her memory. As she recovers from amnesia, she gradually falls for the Singaporean cop who is taking care of her, but is torn when her boyfriend arrives from Australia to take her back.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?663052</url></doc>
